Chipotle Mexican Grill

Chipotle Mexican Grill is a well-known fast casual chain recognized for its emphasis on quality

ingredients and a dining experience that balances speed with authenticity. Customers are often drawn

to Chipotle Mexican Grill because of its consistent focus on freshness, transparency in sourcing, and

the ability to customize meals. Like many in the segment, Chipotle Mexican Grill blends quick service

with higher quality offerings compared to traditional fast food.
